:44.000Z","msg":"喺<br />\n1. 表示時間或者地點。<br />\n【例：表示時間】啟德機場喺1998年今日正式關閉。<br />\n【例：表示地點】我唔想再喺伊個地方再留多半秒鐘。<br />\n2. 表示動作進行緊，常見於「喺道」<br />\n【例】你喺道做緊乜嘢嗟？<br />\n<a href=\"https://incubator.wikimedia.org/wiki/Wt/yue/%E5%96%BA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fincubator.wikimedia.org%2Fwiki%2FWt%2Fyue%2F%25E5%2596%25BA&d=MBLLgfJYEfumY1yC02AkacmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=b3c896f1\" target=\"_blank\">https://incubator.wikimedia.org/wiki/Wt/yue/%E5%96%BA</a><br />\n<br />\n係<br />\n（文言文，粵語，客家）是<br />\n烏龍茶係茶嘅一種。 [廣東話，繁體]<br />\nWu1lung2caa4 hai6 caa4 ge3 jat1 zung2. [粵拼]<br />\n烏龍茶是茶的一種。<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wiktionary.org/zh-hant/%E4%BF%82\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wiktionary.org%2Fzh-hant%2F%25E4%25BF%2582&d=MBLLgfJYEfumY1yC02AkacmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=99fb8ccf\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wiktionary.org/zh-hant/%E4%BF%82</a><br />\n<br />\n雖然樓主想捍衛正嘅苦心係好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但建議樓主唔好咁衝動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己做吓資料搜集先呢就可以減少出錯機會嘞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39f4698c50ff83fc3df1eb477d26a470dba87cfc","tid":562711,"uid":171866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T10:21:47.000Z","msg":"已friend zone,條女同你無感覺先可以同你好理咁溝通，無謂再訓身了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24f9afe3a151799dad7ff0dfe658a5330d7f10dc","tid":562711,"uid":53840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T10:46:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>已friend zone,條女同你無感覺先可以同你好理咁溝通，無謂再訓身了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n對 點頭是岸<br />\n<br />\n屌你 係好撚鍾意嘅 就追啦<br />\n但都等佢分手先<br />\n先保持距離"},{"pid":"0e64ad1b386a6855227fa688ea68bcceb4e250c1","tid":562711,"uid":53840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T11:00:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>已friend zone,條女同你無感覺先可以同你好理咁溝通，無謂再訓身了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n對 回頭是岸<br />\n<br />\n屌你 係好撚鍾意嘅 就追啦<br />\n但都等佢分手先<br />\n先保持距離</blockquote>"}]}